import seaborn as sns
from sklearn.ensemble import AdaBoostClassifier
from sklearn.impute import SimpleImputer
from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score, confusion_matrix
from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split

# Handle missing values using SimpleImputer
imputer = SimpleImputer(strategy='mean') 
trainX_imputed = imputer.fit_transform(trainX)
testX_imputed = imputer.transform(testX)

# Create an AdaBoost Classifier
adaboost_model = AdaBoostClassifier(n_estimators=100, random_state=42)

# Fit the model on the training data
adaboost_model.fit(trainX_imputed, trainY)

# Make predictions on the test set
predictions_adaboost = adaboost_model.predict(testX_imputed)
predicted_prob_adaboost = adaboost_model.predict_proba(testX_imputed)[:, 1]

# Evaluate the performance
accuracy_adaboost = accuracy_score(testY, predictions_adaboost)
print("Accuracy (AdaBoost): {:.4f}".format(accuracy_adaboost))

# Create a confusion matrix
conf_matrix_adaboost = confusion_matrix(testY, predictions_adaboost)

# Display the confusion matrix
plt.figure(figsize=(8, 6))
sns.heatmap(conf_matrix_adaboost, annot=True, fmt="d", cmap="Blues", xticklabels=['No blood pressure 0', 'Blood Pressure 1'], yticklabels=['No blood pressure 0', 'Blood Pressure 1'])
plt.xlabel('Predicted')
plt.ylabel('True')
plt.title('Confusion Matrix - AdaBoost')
plt.show()

Accuracy (AdaBoost): 0.6533
In [73]:
from sklearn.metrics import (
    accuracy_score,
    confusion_matrix,
    precision_score,
    recall_score,
    f1_score,
    roc_auc_score
)
from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split

# Handle missing values using SimpleImputer
imputer = SimpleImputer(strategy='mean') 
trainX_imputed = imputer.fit_transform(trainX)
testX_imputed = imputer.transform(testX)

# Create an AdaBoost Classifier
adaboost_model = AdaBoostClassifier(n_estimators=100, random_state=42)

# Fit the model on the training data
adaboost_model.fit(trainX_imputed, trainY)

# Make predictions on the test set
predictions_adaboost = adaboost_model.predict(testX_imputed)
predicted_prob_adaboost = adaboost_model.predict_proba(testX_imputed)[:, 1]

# Evaluate the performance
accuracy_adaboost = accuracy_score(testY, predictions_adaboost)
precision_adaboost = precision_score(testY, predictions_adaboost)
recall_adaboost = recall_score(testY, predictions_adaboost)
f1_adaboost = f1_score(testY, predictions_adaboost)
roc_auc_adaboost = roc_auc_score(testY, predicted_prob_adaboost)

# Print additional metrics
print("Accuracy (AdaBoost): {:.4f}".format(accuracy_adaboost))
print("Precision (AdaBoost): {:.4f}".format(precision_adaboost))
print("Recall (AdaBoost): {:.4f}".format(recall_adaboost))
print("F1 Score (AdaBoost): {:.4f}".format(f1_adaboost))
print("AUC (AdaBoost): {:.4f}".format(roc_auc_adaboost))

Accuracy (AdaBoost): 0.6533
Precision (AdaBoost): 0.6540
Recall (AdaBoost): 0.4878
F1 Score (AdaBoost): 0.5588
AUC (AdaBoost): 0.6960
